---
import Layout from "~/layouts/PageLayout.astro";


const title = `Terms of Use and Privacy`;
---

<Layout meta={{ title }}>
<main>
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-16 lg:py-20 mx-auto">
  <article>
    <header>
      <h1
        class="px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-5xl md:text-[3.50rem] font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-6 md:mb-8"
      >
       {"{"} Terms and Privacy  || Termos e Privacidade {"}"}
      </h1>
    </header>
    <p class="en uppercase font-mono text-md text-center font-bold">{"{"} en {"}"}</p>
        <div
      class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-3xl prose prose-lg lg:prose-xl dark:prose-invert dark:prose-headings:text-slate-300 prose-md prose-headings:leading-tighter prose-headings:tracking-tighter prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-blue-600 dark:prose-a:text-blue-400 prose-img:rounded-md prose-img:shadow-lg mt-8"
    >
      <p>I did not collect any personal information basides your email if you subscribe to my newsletter. Every email sent will have a link to unsubscribe.</p>
      <p>I use Google Analytics to get visit numbers. The demographic data I has access is sampled and anonymized.</p>
      <p>As Amazon associate for Amazon.com.br I receive for qualified purchases in the Brazil shop.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center line mt-6">--------------------------</div>
    <p class="br uppercase font-mono text-md text-center font-bold mt-3">{"{"} pt-br {"}"}</p>
    <div
      class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-3xl prose prose-lg lg:prose-xl dark:prose-invert dark:prose-headings:text-slate-300 prose-md prose-headings:leading-tighter prose-headings:tracking-tighter prose-headings:font-bold prose-a:text-blue-600 dark:prose-a:text-blue-400 prose-img:rounded-md prose-img:shadow-lg mt-8"
    >
      <p>Eu não coleto nenhuma informação sensível, além do seu e-mail, caso queira se inscrever em minha newsletter pessoal. Todos os emails enviados possuem um link para retirr-se do cadastro a qualquer momento.</p>
      <p>Utilizo o Google Analytics para coletar dados de visita. Dados demográficos são disponibilizados para mim apenas de forma anonimizada e baseada em um recorte.</p>
      <p>Como associado da Amazon, eu recebo por compras qualificadas.</p>
    </div>
    </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>